01:27:37,080 --> 01:27:42,234
# I only see you disappear

1181
01:27:43,920 --> 01:27:50,712
# I know you've got a lot to do
The whole wide world just waits for you

1182
01:27:50,800 --> 01:27:55,430
# And baby, I'll be waiting too

1183
01:27:57,880 --> 01:28:02,192
# He was born to love her, yeah

1184
01:28:03,960 --> 01:28:06,394
# Baby

1185
01:28:06,480 --> 01:28:09,836
# Rescue me

1186
01:28:09,920 --> 01:28:13,469
# Would you, please

1187
01:28:13,560 --> 01:28:21,558
# Just fall out of the sky and rescue me?

1188
01:28:24,480 --> 01:28:29,508
My God! You really do have superpowers.

1189
01:28:29,600 --> 01:28:33,036
Yeah. Well, it helps
when you haven't used them

1190
01:28:33,120 --> 01:28:39,389
in two years, three months,
one week and four days.

1191
01:28:39,480 --> 01:28:43,234
OK, now. I got one more in me. Here we go.

1192
01:28:43,760 --> 01:28:47,719
# Everyday people like you and me

